data.description: 2BED/2BATH LOG HOME for sale in the beautiful Appalachian Mountains! This log home is sure to impress. From your full covered rocking shair front porch, you walk into the nice sized great room with woodburning fireplace for those cozy evenings. In the back of the house is the dining with doors leading to the covered back porch. Next to the dining room is the tastefully designed kitchen. You'll find the stack washer/dryer opposite the kitchen. The main level bedroom and bath complete the main floor. Upstairs, you are greeted by a loft sitting area, another bedroom and bathroom. The beautiful wood cathedral ceilings throughout are a sight to behold! The house is on a private well and has a metal roof & separate outbuilding. Easy access from state maintained road and only minutes to downtown Murphy, or Blue Ridge, GA! The mountains are calling!
